description: This sentence specifies a work-time requirement for employees on Saturdays. It verifies that employees have put in their working hours between 9:00 AM and 3:30 PM, taking into consideration a 1-hour break. This ensures that employees have met the schedule for a Saturday shift, maintaining a balance between their work hours and the designated break time.
